OL,7,FWatch the moment that coastguard
OL,8,Fvessels belonging to China and the
OL,9,FPhilippines collide in the South China
OL,10,FSea (Credit: Philippine Coast Guard)
OL,12,Fand coastguard vessels have been
OL,13,Ffilmed colliding into each other in a
OL,14,Fdisputed section of the .
OL,16,FFootage released by the Philippine
OL,17,FCoast Guard (PCG) showed its BRP
OL,18,FSindangan vessel making contact with a
OL,19,FChinese coastguard patrol boat on
OL,20,FTuesday.
