OL,7,FThe BRP Sindangan suffered minor
OL,8,Fstructural damage, the PCG said,
OL,9,Fbefore a separate collision between
OL,10,FChinese and Filipino boats took place
OL,11,Fa short while later.
OL,13,FThat same vessel was later targeted by
OL,14,FChinese water cannons, shattering its
OL,15,Fwindshields and injuring at least four
OL,16,FFilipino crew members, according to
OL,17,Fthe Philippine government taskforce
OL,18,Fdealing with territorial disputes.
