OL,7,FThe incidents took place off the
OL,8,Fdisputed Second Thomas Shoal, which
OL,9,Fboth the Philippines and China lay
OL,10,Fclaim to.
OL,12,FChina's deputy ambassador was
OL,13,Fsummoned, in the wake of the
OL,14,Fincidents, by the Philippine
OL,15,FDepartment of Foreign Affairs to
OL,16,Fconvey a protest against the Chinese
OL,17,Fcoastguard's actions.
