OL,7,F"The Philippines demands that Chinese
OL,8,Fvessels leave the vicinity of Ayungin
OL,9,Fshoal (Filipino name for the shoal)
OL,10,Fimmediately," the department said in a
OL,11,Fstatement.
OL,13,FA small Philippine marine and navy
OL,14,Fcontingent has kept watch onboard a
OL,15,Frusting Second World War ship, the BRP
OL,16,FSierra Madre, which has been marooned
OL,17,Fsince the late 1990s in the shallows
OL,18,Fof the Second Thomas Shoal.
