OL,7,FChina has long contested the
OL,8,FPhilippines' territorial claim,
OL,9,Fsurrounding the shoal with coastguard
OL,10,Fand naval vessels to prevent
OL,11,FPhilippine forces from delivering
OL,12,Fconstruction materials to fortify the
OL,13,FSierra Madre.
OL,15,FChina's coastguard said in a statement
OL,16,Fthat "it took control measures in
OL,17,Faccordance with the law against
OL,18,FPhilippine ships that illegally
OL,19,Fintruded into the waters adjacent to
OL,20,FRen'ai Reef (Chinese name for the
OL,21,Fshoal)".
